trans-unit.source: Represents dependencies returned by the build manager.
trans-unit.target: Representa as dependências retornadas pelo Gerenciador de compilação.

trans-unit.source: The BuildDependencySet object for an application can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildManager.GetCachedBuildDependencySet%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: O objeto BuildDependencySet para um aplicativo pode ser recuperado por meio de <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildManager.GetCachedBuildDependencySet%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildManager.GetCachedBuildDependencySet%2A>

trans-unit.source: It contains the properties that represent the list of dependencies.
trans-unit.target: Ele contém as propriedades que representam a lista de dependências.

trans-unit.source: Gets a string representing the hash code of the dependent virtual paths.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma cadeia de caracteres que representa o código de hash de caminhos virtuais dependentes.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> representing the hash code of the dependent virtual paths.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.String>que representa o código de hash de caminhos virtuais dependentes.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets a list of virtual path dependencies.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma lista de dependências do caminho virtual.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> containing the virtual path dependencies.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>que contém as dependências de caminho virtual.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>
